title: CICaidA SBDC Presentaion
subtitle: This Presenation was created and used for the Small Buisness Development Center Competition
Overview: For the SBDC competition, a team of three individuals, including myself, was assembled  to create a business model and proposal for the Stony Brook University Research project CICaidA. The presentation was then used to compete in the Small Business Development Competition, where it was presented to a live panel of business entrepreneurs and expert judges. Our presentation and post Q&A session were awarded second place in the competition and received grant money to continue development of the project.
